Insider Activity


Individual




Marc Taxay



Mr. Marc Taxay is Senior Vice President & General Counsel at Arista Networks, Inc., a Member at Pennsylvania State Bar Association and a Member at The State Bar of California. Mr. Taxay was previously employed as Senior Vice President & General Counsel by MedeAnalytics, Inc., a Principal by Cohen & Grigsby PC, Assistant General Counsel by Coremetrics, Inc., a Principal by Pepper Hamilton LLP, and a Principal by Wilson Sonsini Goodrich & Rosati PC. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Michigan and a graduate degree from the University of Michigan.



